@0 = ~All of them are out to get me, they think I don't know, but I do.~
@1 = ~They're the ones that got me thrown in here, all them conspired to have me put away.~
@2 = ~Soon my revenge will come... very soon.~
@3 = ~Never underestimate the power of hate, it keeps a man warm inside.~
@4 = ~Everyone around me is a traitor and liar, they steal my thoughts to make me suffer! But I have secret thoughts they will never find!~
@5 = ~I see they have finally come to murder me, shut me up, make their problems go away. Well I wont let them, no I will make them swim in their own blood.~
